JOSH TAYLOR 


== Headline text ==
Josh Taylor was born on [[15 November]] [[1991]] and is the son of [[God]]. Josh goes to [[Varndean]] School in [[Brighton]] and gets regularly rejected by his friends and girls he fancies. This is not fair to Josh as he is not a [[chav]], nor is he an [[emo]]. What Josh looks for in a woman is someone who looks like Justine Frischmann and is passionate about Blur and The Smiths]] (who are by the way, the two best bands ever)

